  <div class="page"> <img class="p_img" src="/assets/fullwidth.jpg" width="1050" />
    <div class="leftcontent">
      <div class="uppercontent"> <span>Contact</span><span class="boldclass"> Us</span>
        <p>Like what you see? Have a question or comment? Like to advertise? Shoot us a quick message.</p>
        <div>
